			<node ID="ID_634204135" TEXT="Kerberos is a system of authentication developed at MIT as part of the Athena project. Kerberos uses encryption technology and a trusted third party an arbitrator to perform secure authentication on an open network. Specifically Kerberos uses cryptographic tickets in order to avoid transmitting plain text passwords over the wire." />
