			</node>
		<node ID="ID_883515979" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kerberos_(moon)" TEXT="Kerberos (moon) - Wikipedia">
			<node ID="ID_108704295" TEXT="Kerberos is a small natural satellite of Pluto about 19 km (12 mi) in its longest dimension.It was the fourth moon of Pluto to be discovered and its existence was announced on 20 July 2011. It was imaged along with Pluto and its four other moons by the New Horizons spacecraft in July 2015. The first image of Kerberos was released to the public on 22 October 2015." />
