		<node ID="ID_819999197" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kerberos_%28protocol%29" TEXT="Kerberos (protocol) - Wikipedia">
			<node ID="ID_1045345512" TEXT="Kerberos (/ &#712; k &#604;&#720;r b &#601;r &#594; s /) is a computer-network authentication protocol that works on the basis of tickets to allow nodes communicating over a non-secure network to prove their identity to one another in a secure manner. The protocol was named after the character Kerberos (or Cerberus) from Greek mythology the ferocious three-headed guard dog of Hades." />
